loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a1 = random(2,10,1);
$i1 = random(1,7,1);
$b1 = random(2,11,1);
$c1 = 2*$a1 - $b1 + $i1;
##need 2$a1 < $b1 + $c1;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The inequality \(2 x+ $a1 \leq x + $b1 \leq 3x +$c1 \) means that \( x \) is in
the closed interval \( [A,B] \) where \( A \) is:
\{ans_rule(20) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = ($b1-$c1)/2;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
and  \( B \) is:
\{ans_rule(20) \}
$BR
EOT

$ans = $b1-$a1;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

